id=gemini-cli
name=Antigravity/Gemini CLI Systemless Support
version=v2.0
versionCode=2
author=mino
description=Provides systemless auto-patching native Antigravity CLI (agy) support on Android ARM64 with 39-bit VA space. Includes glibc shim routing, TCMalloc binary patching, systemless hosts DNS bypass, and boot-time permissive SELinux. Also supports legacy Gemini CLI via Node.js.
